comments.body:
Can you add JSON Schema validation? We accept user data here, so we cannot trust this data to be correct, so we should validate it.
```json
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "ignored_rules": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "custom_rules": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
```
